{"tid":1942063,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Charley考考你：經典文宣知多少","createTime":"2020-03-24T23:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T09:03:00.000Z","uid":257665,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"14ef16ff74eaf874ae8286009d2983bbbe0385df","tid":1942063,"uid":257665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n21pimg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn21pimg.png&h=231ef678&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見就見得多，但你地又知道以下呢啲經典文宣幾多？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/axnPusY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaxnPusY.png&h=f3fc4663&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問. 呢幅勇武女抗爭者係借鏡邊個作品? A. 中華英雄 B. 平成聖母 C. 洛神賦圖<br />\n答. <strong>B. 畫法係借鏡大友昇平作品「平成聖母」。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">作者係芥蘭炒雞蛋 (我們由2019開始的夢遊)<br />\n🐧🔎 <a href=\"https://charleywong.giffon.io/Kailanegg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharleywong.giffon.io%2FKailanegg&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=f9d02666\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charleywong.giffon.io/Kailanegg</a><br />\n呢幅畫喺「葵芳連儂美術館」出現後聲名大噪。最近仲有人印左喺貨車頂！<br />\n後面果8個毛筆字係來自 (Instagram) @nonsleepcalligraphy 嘅作品。<br />\n留意返作者有提到大家可隨意在網上分享或製成免費物品派發，但商用義賣籌款等等要先得作者同意。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WL2zFzF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWL2zFzF.png&h=b096a2e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問. 香港加油90度翻轉字作者係邊度人? A. 香港 B. 日本 C. 臺灣<br />\n答. <strong>C. 作者為臺灣博方文創藝術總監馬賽Kyo (往地球出發吧-馬賽kyo的旅行圖與文)</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">🐧🔎 <a href=\"https://charleywong.giffon.io/iam_kyo_chen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharleywong.giffon.io%2Fiam_kyo_chen&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=db84384b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charleywong.giffon.io/iam_kyo_chen</a><br />\n「香港加油」從2019年6月至今，一直出現於各個抗爭產品同文宣上：蛋糕，鎖匙扣，紋身，咩都有。<br />\n作者有開放大眾申請免費授權，注意都係要問過先用！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zS1HPs2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzS1HPs2.png&h=f0ee213e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問. 招財進寶/追求自由民主翻轉字作者又係邊度人? A. 香港 B. 日本 C. 臺灣<br />\n答. <strong>C. 都係臺灣，但係唔係香港加油果個。創作人係林國慶翻轉文字 (著作權持有者為魔翻文創)。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">🐧🔎 <a href=\"https://charleywong.giffon.io/hellojoking\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharleywong.giffon.io%2Fhellojoking&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=ca3cf0b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charleywong.giffon.io/hellojoking</a><br />\n新年時經常見到嘅翻轉揮春。要使用的話要得到書面正式授權。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hXYV9s4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhXYV9s4.png&h=a9b8b55a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問. 如果想俾錢 download 正版願榮光歸香港 album (12 tracks)，要幾錢？A. $7 B. $70 C. $270<br />\n答. <strong>B. 喺官方 bandcamp 買的話係 $70。其實同去黃店食一餐差唔多。野食就食一次，歌就可以聽完又聽，抵！另外除左bandcamp，Apple Music 都有官方 album。</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">作者係願榮光歸香港 Dgx原創團隊 (湯瑪仕與眾香港人)：<br />\n🐧🔎 <a href=\"https://charleywong.giffon.io/glorytohkdgx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharleywong.giffon.io%2Fglorytohkdgx&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=75c87f23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charleywong.giffon.io/glorytohkdgx</a><br />\n遊行集會甚至喺部分黃店都會聽到嘅歌曲。創作團隊 YouTube 上面有好多高質嘅 music videos，其實都使左好多錢喺錄音製作。大家要支持佢地，去買返佢地官方推出嘅正版歌同周邊！都係果句，如果要用首歌或者歌詞，要先得到授權！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iS87f76.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiS87f76.png&h=78970aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小豬問. &ldquo;點解佢地唔一齊嚟？&rdquo;<br />\n黑衣人答. <strong>&ldquo;因為佢地會永遠幫我地守護住2019年嘅香港&rdquo;</strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">作者係 Watchit觀賞用：<br />\n🐧🔎 <a href=\"https://charleywong.giffon.io/watchit.comics\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharleywong.giffon.io%2Fwatchit.comics&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=62b0ba61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charleywong.giffon.io/watchit.comics</a><br />\n一月一號流傳於社交網絡嘅催淚文宣。或者未有大師級畫功，但果份純真深深打動到 Charley！話說作者有出抗爭吉祥物 stickers, 大家不妨 download 嚟用。記得 like &amp; follow 返作者！留意返作者有提到所有圖片不供商業用途。</span><br />\n<br />\n今次問住五題先，遲啲仲有㗎！<br />\n求 like Charley Wong 和你查 FB page <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/charleywong2020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcharleywong2020&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2Byn8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=52bfc8fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/charleywong2020</a>"},{"pid":"f6e921a53718ed131e03d16a688455cf7c6913ee","tid":1942063,"uid":5298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:23:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3476a02e14c6ae9f43ef9cd72764c0f92139ffcd","tid":1942063,"uid":254028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e886d735b509b95307af1be9f987c3f87364949d","tid":1942063,"uid":65932,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:31:34.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb9cc45f682d6721c3db67d59cd1fea9502e0c0","tid":1942063,"uid":327953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd040926c794e9b4de5b895d03a56aee0a87fc98","tid":1942063,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-24T23:46:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b97746055122b521714f76e9bd2920a8a85dc